			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Hello fellow necros.<BR>
<BR>
This spell at first might seem a bit far off and useless.... But when you think, it can be quite kool for battling yellow or low red undead critters.  At lvl 17, pull a DB with darkness, send in pet, cast hungry earth to root the undead DB skel. Once it is rooted, back your pet off and cast this on it and cast Heat blood.  Once done, send pet back in.  The DB should be dead quite soon after using this combo.  I have seen this done many times in oasis by a soloing necro.  He said he could do this and still have about half of his mana in pool for a lesser critter to take right after the DB before medding.<BR>
<BR>
My 2pp,<BR>
<BR>
BobSarducci:lvl 14 DE necro on Cazic-Thule server.
